column16: Daniel Murphy hits a grand slam (24) to right field.   Danny Espinosa scores.    Clint Robinson scores.    Jayson Werth scores.
Jayson Werth walks.   Danny Espinosa to 3rd.    Clint Robinson to 2nd.
Clint Robinson singles on a ground ball to right fielder Nolan Reimold.   Danny Espinosa to 2nd.
Danny Espinosa singles on a ground ball to third baseman Manny Machado.
Ryan Zimmerman flies out to right fielder Nolan Reimold.
Wilson Ramos flies out to center fielder Adam Jones.
Anthony Rendon flies out to center fielder Adam Jones.
Alex Bregman called out on strikes.
George Springer flies out to left fielder Nolan Reimold.
Teoscar Hernandez singles on a soft fly ball to left fielder Nolan Reimold.
Marwin Gonzalez bunt grounds out, catcher Francisco Pena to first baseman Steve Pearce.
Jake Marisnick homers (3) on a fly ball to left field.
Tony Kemp lines out to center fielder Adam Jones.
